OL,3,CLondon Mayor backs under-16s ban on
OL,4,Csocial media
OL,6,FLondon Mayor Sir Sadiq Khan has backed
OL,7,Fa ban on social media for under-16s,
OL,8,Fsaying it is "the only way to stem the
OL,9,Fharms we know are happening right now".
OL,11,FCampaigners, including bereaved
OL,12,Fparents of children whose deaths were
OL,13,Flinked to social media, have called on
OL,14,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer to
OL,15,Fbring in an Australia-style ban.
OL,17,FThe Government's consultation on
OL,18,Fchildren's online experiences ` which
OL,19,Ffloated measures such as a ban for
OL,20,Funder-16s, app curfews and limits on
OL,21,Faddictive features ` closed last week.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
