OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780423900
OL,3,CLondon Mayor backs under-16s ban on
OL,4,Csocial media
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister has promised to
OL,7,Ftake "game-changer" action on the
OL,8,Fissue and vowed to move quickly, but
OL,9,Fhe has not yet promised a ban on under-
OL,10,F16s accessing social media.
OL,12,FHis Labour Party colleague Sir Sadiq
OL,13,Fhas previously said the impact of
OL,14,FAustralia's ban should be monitored,
OL,15,Fbut is now publicly backing such a
OL,16,Fmeasure.
OL,26,@oD@FOUoD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
