PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780423900
OL,3,CLondon Mayor backs under-16s ban on
OL,4,Csocial media
OL,6,FLondon's mayor, giving a speech in the
OL,7,Fcapital on Tuesday to an audience of
OL,8,Fengineers, founders and investors,
OL,9,Fsaid tech firms must prove their
OL,10,Fservices are safe for children or face
OL,11,Fa ban on being available to under-16s.
OL,13,FHe said: "I don't think children
OL,14,Fshould be on social media.
OL,16,F"From food to pharmaceuticals, almost
OL,17,Fevery company has to prove that its
OL,18,Fproducts are safe before they're sold.
OL,19,FI see no reason why social media firms
OL,20,Fshouldn't do the same.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780423900
OL,3,CLondon Mayor backs under-16s ban on
OL,4,Csocial media
OL,6,F"Until they can prove that their
OL,7,Fplatforms are safe for kids, a ban is
OL,8,Fthe only way to stem the harms we know
OL,9,Fare happening right now."
OL,11,FBut Sir Sadiq also added that a ban
OL,12,Falone will not solve all the issues,
OL,13,Fwarning: "Rather than just restricting
OL,14,Faccess to social media, we must
OL,15,Freimagine it."
OL,17,F"Londoners deserve platforms which
OL,18,Fprioritise people, not just profit,
OL,19,Fwhere connection does not carry such a
OL,20,Fheavy cost."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@YO]uD@JOUwD@NO]yD@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
