PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780423900
OL,3,CLondon Mayor backs under-16s ban on
OL,4,Csocial media
OL,6,FHe called on tech companies to
OL,7,F"explain how misogyny spreads like
OL,8,Fwildfire on their platforms ` and
OL,9,Fpublicly set out how they'll adjust
OL,10,Ftheir algorithms to stop it.
OL,12,F"If they refuse to act, then the state
OL,13,Fmust step up."
OL,15,FA survey of 222 boys in London
OL,16,Fconducted by phone network provider EE
OL,17,Ffound that 12% of under-16s had been
OL,18,Fexposed to harmful masculinity
OL,19,Fmessaging daily, and a further 32% on
OL,20,Fa weekly basis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
