CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780423900
OL,3,CLondon Mayor backs under-16s ban on
OL,4,Csocial media
OL,6,FAashraya Karki, a 17-year-old speaking
OL,7,Fto ITV News at a grassroots football
OL,8,Fevent explained: "A lot of terms from
OL,9,Fthe manosphere, like sigma and alpha
OL,10,Fhave spread like wildfire.
OL,12,F"Toxic masculinity can really
OL,13,Fsegregate friend groups - I saw many
OL,14,Fsplit based on the lines influencers
OL,15,Fwere preaching.
OL,17,F"I think a total ban would not be
OL,18,Fbeneficial, but limiting how much of
OL,19,Fthat negative influence is brought out
OL,20,Fin social media would be beneficial."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
