PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780423900
OL,3,CLondon Mayor backs under-16s ban on
OL,4,Csocial media
OL,6,FIn his speech on Tuesday, Sir Sadiq
OL,7,FKhan insisted the "era of impunity is
OL,8,Fover" and that tech firms must "must
OL,9,Fface the consequences" if they cannot
OL,10,Fprotect people on their platforms.
OL,12,FHe announced a #1 million package of
OL,13,Fmeasures to support boys and young men
OL,14,Facross the capital, and warned that
OL,15,Fonline misogyny risks "a lost
OL,16,Fgeneration of young men".
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@EO]pD@`OUqD@VO]wD@WOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780423900
OL,3,CLondon Mayor backs under-16s ban on
OL,4,Csocial media
OL,6,FHe branded so-called manosphere
OL,7,Finfluencers "snake oil salesmen who
OL,8,Ftake advantage of young men's ambition
OL,9,Fto peddle pound shop misogyny," adding
OL,10,Fthat misogynistic content can be
OL,11,F"catastrophic for the young men who
OL,12,Fconsume it" and have "terrifying"
OL,13,Fconsequences for the women close to
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,FWarning of a system "rigged" in favour
OL,17,Fof such harmful voices online, he
OL,18,Fclaimed such voices are not only being
OL,19,F"allowed to pump out poison" but
OL,20,Frewarded for it.
OL,26,@oD@MOUqD@_O]sD@AOUtD@KO]tD@VOUtD@aO]xD@
OL,26,AUOUxD@\O]{D@AOU{D@\O]
